room_title: Escape room "The Hospital of Horror" by Escape Room NJ in New York
room_description: Prepare to be Scared…enter the Hospital of Horror, where you never know what is lurking around the corner….what you will see on the next floor or even more terrifying what you could not see….until it was too late. Suspend your notions of what is “not real” or “impossible”….as once you enter our Virtual Reality your reality may never be the same!
